(19115, 46, 249, 6, 'I Still Call Your Name', '', '2008-04-04 00:00:00', 2008, 15, 0, 7, 'I know every chance I pray\r\nI know every word you say\r\nEvery moment here I could understand\r\n \r\nTell me what''s the end\r\nIt may be over the hate\r\nTell me if I could\r\n(Tell me if I''m here)\r\nI still call your name\r\n\r\nAs long as I still stay\r\nAs long as I still wait\r\n                                                                                \r\n(Chorus)\r\nWhat if you think you know\r\n(where is our home)\r\nWhat if you say so cold\r\n(where is our warm)\r\nWhat if you always fall into the hole\r\n \r\nAs long as I still plan\r\nAs long as I still wait\r\n', '', 288, '', '王如江', '王如江', '王如江', 'BFWSP', '', 1, 1, 0, '2009-09-17 12:45:56', '2015-03-12 13:40:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
